      "text": "Pehz to buhs tam Pree-\nsteram schohs Lahstus Grahma-\nta rakſtihf / un ar to ruhktu Uh-\ndeni noskalloht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſcham buhs to ruhk-\ntu/ to nolahdetu Uhdeni tai See-\nwai dsert doht/ ta ka tas nolah-\ndets Uhdens winnai par Ruhk-\ntun u ee-eet.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 25,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tam Preesteram buhs\nno tahs Seewas Rohkas to\nDuſinoſchanas - Uppuri xemt /\nun par Ehdami - Uppuri kuſti-\nnaht preekſch to KUNGA/ un to\nus to Altari uppureht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 26,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tam Preesteram buhs\nno ta Ehdama - Uppura weenu\npilnu Sanju par Peeminneſcha-\nnas Uppuri kampt / un to us to\nAltari eededſinaht / un pehz to\nbuhs winnam to Uhdent tai See-\nwai dsert doht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 27,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Kad uu wiꞥſch to Uhdenti\nwinnai irr dsert dewis / tad tas\nnotiks/ja ta irr fagahnijufees/un\nprett fawn Wihrn noseegdances\nirr noseegufees / ka tas nolah-\ndets Uhdens winnai par Ruhktu-\nmu buhs / un winnas Wehders\nustuhfs/ un winnas Ziska fakrit-\ntihs/ un ta patti Seewa buhs par\nLahtu starp faweem Laudin.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 28,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Bet ja ta Seewa ne irr\nfagahnijufees/ bet fschkikſta/ tad\nbuhs winna wefela/ un angliga.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 29,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Schi irr to Paulibas-Duſ-\nmoschanu Bauſliba / kad weena\nlaulata Seewa irr nowehrſufees/\nun fagahnijufees.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 30,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jeb kad pahr weenu Wihr-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "ru tas Duſinoſchanas - Gare\nnahk/ un wiꞥſch pahr fawn See-\nwu duſino / ka tam ta Seewa-\njawedd KUNGA Preekſchā / un\nka tam Preesteram wiſta feh-\nBauſliba pee tahs jadarra.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 31,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad buhs tas Wihrs na-\nta Noseeguina nenoseedsigs/ be-\ntai Seewai buhs fawn Noseegu-\nimu nest.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ta VI. Voballa.\nDeewa Likkumi preekſch teem Nasareereem / ka-\nDeewam foſlijahs : 1 / 2. Ka tohs attka-\nbuhs fchfihſtihf : 9. Uk no tahs paſchas Ap-\nfohlischanas atswabbinaht : 13. Tee Sweh-\ntischanas Wahrbi/ kas teem Preestereem paſh-\nteem Laudim jarunna: 22.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "N tas KUNGS runna-\nja us Mohsu/un fazzija:\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Runna us teem\nIsraeta Behrneem / un fakki us\nteem : Kad kahds Wihrs/jeb See-\nwa apfohliahfs weens * Nasaree-\nris buht/ gribbedans tam KUN-\nGAM fawadi turretees.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "* Nasareeris irr tik dauds, ka weens Atschkir-\ntajs, kas no Pafaules Darbeem fchkirrahs, un us\nDeewa Dohmahin un fwehteem Darbeem doh-\ndahs. Tahdi bija weena Preekſch-Sihme us to\nKungu Jelu : luuk Sohg Gr: 13, 5. Raud: Df:\n3, 7. Amos: 2, 11.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tami buhs no Wihrn un-\nstipra Dsehreena fargatees/ Wihr-\nna-Ettiki un stipra Dsehreena Et-\ntiki tam ne buhs dsert / nedg-\nsattas / nedg faunsas Wihrna-Oh-\ngas ehft.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Zik tigi tas irr apfohlieces/\ntam ne buhs ehft no wiſa / kas\nno ta Wihrna-Kohka tohp taſtihts/\nno Kohdoſa libds Sehnalabm.\n"
    },
